  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Roast the garlic and ginger in the oven for 10 minutes.",
    "Slice the preserved lemon and add it to the roasted garlic and ginger.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper to the mixture.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a lacquerware bowl over medium heat.",
    "Add the baby plum tomatoes to the bowl and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the roasted garlic and ginger mixture to the tomatoes and stir to combine.",
    "Simmer the tagine for 20 minutes or until the tomatoes are tender.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
